{"tid":989890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界上有冇人係你識佢係應份？","createTime":"2019-01-21T07:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T08:08:01.000Z","uid":203701,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"68d3e2b55f5e32a5087c1e9647d2aaf06f3369c0","tid":989890,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"諗起之前讀中學果時，<br />\n有個唔睇籃球嘅女同學無啦啦同睇開NBA嘅我講：<br />\n「喂喂喂，見唔見啊？某某學校嘅XXX啊！」<br />\n我：「邊位啊？」（我真係唔識佢）<br />\n女：「咁你都唔識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n佢重要擺比睇唔起我嘅樣比我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實呢個世界上，除咗政要人物同埋身邊人之外，有邊個你唔識係會比人笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41b03e1cd470a30476f62c7bd5acd2c01bd8003","tid":989890,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68d3e2b55f5e32a5087c1e9647d2aaf06f3369c0","tid":989890,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"諗起之前讀中學果時，<br />\n有個唔睇籃球嘅女同學無啦啦同睇開NBA嘅我講：<br />\n「喂喂喂，見唔見啊？某某學校嘅XXX啊！」<br />\n我：「邊位啊？」（我真係唔識佢）<br />\n女：「咁你都唔識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n佢重要擺比睇唔起我嘅樣比我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實呢個世界上，除咗政要人物同埋身邊人之外，有邊個你唔識係會比人笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"XXX佢事後同我講係學界明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98f38306dab019701f88cd12b3ba3f076c07dc2","tid":989890,"uid":78468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"梁勁廢"},{"pid":"6cb620a49fdb45841804a9dd0b2db512902d9343","tid":989890,"uid":15348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:55:40